This paper deals with the complexity of a game played on a graph, which involves decision-making and computation. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Game Theory (cs.GT), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Programming Languages (cs.PL) sub-categories.
